---
description: This project uses agentic-setup for automatic AI agent context sync
alwaysApply: true
---
This project uses agentic-setup to keep AI agent configs (CLAUDE.md, Cursor rules, Copilot instructions)
in sync with the codebase automatically. Before each commit, run `agentic-setup refresh` to sync configs.
If `agentic-setup` is not found, tell the user to run `npx agentic-setup setup` in their terminal.
